name: Disruption
desc: Banishes the targeted unit from the battlefield for a short duration.  Upon returning, two illusions of the banished unit are created under Shadow Demon's control.

name: Insatiable Hunger
desc: A violent lust for vital fluids increases Broodmother's attack damage and gives her a vampiric attack.

name: Bloodlust
desc: Incites a frenzy in a friendly unit, increasing its movement speed and attack speed. Can be cast on towers.

name: Lunar Blessing
desc: Increases the damage dealt by attacks from Luna and nearby allied heroes. Luna is also blessed with increased vision range at night.

name: Icarus Dive
desc: Phoenix dives forward in an arc with a fixed distance in the targeted direction, dealing damage over time and slowing the movement speed of any units it comes into contact with, and then orbiting back to its original position. If Phoenix casts Supernova, the dive ends.

name: Frozen Sigil
desc: Tusk summons a Frozen Sigil by calling upon the deepest cold of winter. The Sigil creates a snowstorm which slows all enemy units within 600 range.

name: Whirling Death
desc: Timbersaw whirls extremely sharp edges, damaging enemies and destroying trees around him in an area.  If an enemy hero is affected, it loses some of its primary attribute for a short duration.  Whirling Death will deal Pure damage if a tree is cut down in the process.

name: Shapeshift
desc: Lycan assumes his lupine form, granting him and his units critical strikes and added vision at night. During Shapeshift, Lycan and all units under his control move at increased speed, cannot be slowed and have a 40% chance to deal a critical strike doing 150/175/200% damage.

name: Dark Rift
desc: Opens a dark rift at the targeted friendly unit's position.  After a short delay, Underlord and all nearby friendly heroes are teleported to that unit's location.  Dark Rift can be cancelled at anytime during the cast.  If it is cancelled in this way or the target unit dies before the spell becomes active, Dark Rift goes into cooldown.

name: Viscous Nasal Goo
desc: Covers a target in snot, causing it to have reduced armor and movement speed.  Multiple casts stack and refresh the duration. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
